<h1>Setup Access Required</h1>

<p>Your account does not currently have permission to open the Admin area (<code>setup.access</code>).</p>

<p>This can happen if Super Administrator role permissions were changed or the role was inactivated while exploring setup screens.</p>

<h2>Recovery</h2>

<p>An administrator with server access can restore defaults by running:</p>

<pre>docker compose exec web bin/rails db:seed</pre>

<p>Or in the Rails console:</p>

<pre>SuperAdministratorProtection.restore!</pre>

<p><%= link_to "Return to dashboard", root_path %></p>
